			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">BOLTS
<br />

<br />
Try shooting a bolt on anything and you will get aggro. Mobs in PoS, BoT, Nadox and Hate's Fury all have the same thing now. Shoot a bolt, even when the mob is at 10% totally rammed down by a pally or such and you will get the aggro till the next stun / taunt.
<br />

<br />
I can shoot 3 Black Steels on a mob and np, but 1 2k bolt at any time and I get smashed.
<br />

<br />
Several people have seen this now and a guildie encouraged everyone to feedback it.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=39733">Arch Convoker Rhand Drago'Magica</a>
<br />
Husband of Mistress Hebzibah
